  "authorEmail": "simon@simondorfman.com",
  "notes": "Considering these changes:\n-Complete Surprise for Weasel Attack?\n-Oracle of Delphi for Front Lines?\n-Yorgia Sandow for Undead Htimsen?\n-Clockwork Ogre for Quill Pen of the Planes?\n-add Goibhniu's Warhammer?\n\nPhilosophy:\nAim for long-term dominance via constant attack.  Instant win, battle-hearty deck.  Play offensively, attack and raze realms.  Cards that can be used over and over (magic items & artifacts) are prefered to one-use cards.  Except events where the return is generally justified.\n\nChampions:\nInstantly win (but are not instantly defeated like Living Scroll and King of the Elves). AD&D for artifacts.  Dragons for Orb of GreenDragonkind.\n\nCombos:\n-Put Orb of Green Dragonkind on an instant defeat champ and copy Stryck's power to choose defender.\n-Sword and Helm on Undead Htimsen so any Psionicist that defends is defeated\n-Arena, then attack flyer with Gloriana discards them, or attack undead with Corpse Dragon discards them, or attack a non-cleric, -psionicist, -hero and attack Sword and Helm to discard him also.\n-living wall + ego coin + quill pen, copy bilago's power makes him almost unstoppable",
